Postman collection: 
1. http://localhost:8000/auth(post) - for login
2. http://localhost:8000/authreg(post) - for registration
3. http://localhost:8000/check-account - for checking if account exist
4. http://localhost:8000//verify - verify account using jwt token
5. http://localhost:8000//upload - for uploading image in create list
6. http://localhost:8000/upupload - for uploading image in update list
7. http://localhost:8000/api/products/addProduct - adding product in create list
8. http://localhost:8000/api/products/allProducts - retriving all products 
9. http://localhost:8000/api/products/getOne - get one product in search
10. http://localhost:8000/api/products/update/:title - update product
11. http://localhost:8000/api/products/delete - delete product
12. http://localhost:8000/api/products/getProductsbyPids - get product by product id in liked product list.
13. http://localhost:8000/api/users/get - get user by email id in profile 
14. http://localhost:8000/api/lproducts/addlProduct - add product in liked products
15. http://localhost:8000//api/lproducts//allLProducts - get all liked products by user.